 "steam_appid": 3172310, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sex Desert: Mad Lust</strong> opens up the universe of Carnality INC. - a futuristic corporation that provides its clients with a thrill of living out their wildest fantasies set up in the company’s amusement park, filled with ultra-realistic decorations and intelligent android actors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/b8ec05da715043760b9d3de4a0a78921.poster.avif?t=1759347769\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/b8ec05da715043760b9d3de4a0a78921.webm?t=1759347769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/b8ec05da715043760b9d3de4a0a78921.mp4?t=1759347769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/a580383312c2c07d243fe77066c4c365.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist is a client taking off on an adventure set up in a dystopian post-apocalyptic desert split up between the Dictator of religious fanatics and the Rebels - a group of people who don’t go along with a dictatorship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/4b0ed34154a9cb9518f9868ab0d63d49.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=277 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/0ae180f7bdf67b9ba5fa9394ff0446e8.avif?t=1759347769\" width=586 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since you’re the only one who knows every major twist and occurrence of the story in advance, you declare yourself a Prophet and try to establish your own religious authority, opposing the Dictator himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/7dc727ec7062804fd53f88fd9f00e6a5.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=277 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/fbe8fe697f5728003b7f7df8a19ae35b.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/3343fa2c50dbf6bf904e339b7b944a81.poster.avif?t=1759347769\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/3343fa2c50dbf6bf904e339b7b944a81.webm?t=1759347769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/3343fa2c50dbf6bf904e339b7b944a81.mp4?t=1759347769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thanks to being the customer of that madness - you can shape events however you like! Whose side will you take, would you betray them, who’ll be your fellow companions, and who will try to hunt you down? You decide!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/cf5f7ab29214de1e8e6e659d77861d