ras/b8ec05da715043760b9d3de4a0a78921.mp4?t=1759347769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/a580383312c2c07d243fe77066c4c365.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The protagonist is a client taking off on an adventure set up in a dystopian post-apocalyptic desert split up between the Dictator of religious fanatics and the Rebels - a group of people who don’t go along with a dictatorship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/4b0ed34154a9cb9518f9868ab0d63d49.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=277 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/0ae180f7bdf67b9ba5fa9394ff0446e8.avif?t=1759347769\" width=586 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since you’re the only one who knows every major twist and occurrence of the story in advance, you declare yourself a Prophet and try to establish your own religious authority, opposing the Dictator himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/7dc727ec7062804fd53f88fd9f00e6a5.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=277 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172310/extras/fbe8fe697f5728003b7f7df8a19ae35b.avif?t=1759347769\" width=572 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay mu